Text.string: Let's make this an unfair fight.
Resistance is futile, but it is also fun.
Whoever kills that competitor gets a bonus.
Return all scalps to MAL for bonus compensation.
Posing as organic is punishable by death.
Threat assessment. Watch for angry critters.
Attention... soldier... you will be reduced to ash.
Hostile soldier on the field. Correction: extremely hostile.
Danger. Danger. Ursa Corps veteran in play.
Highly-trained Ursa Corps soldier. Liquidate with prejudice.
Recording battle data for internal training purposes.
Please commence shooting at that soldier.
Attention... Operative... you will be reduced to ash.
Mad skills detected. You should work for us.
We will assimilate your toys and sell knockoffs.
We have a few tricks of our own, you know.
You're not as clever as you think.
You have been identified as a narcissist.
What are you even wearing? You look ridiculous.
Attention... Siren... you will be reduced to ash.
Magic is no match for science.
You're not the only who can glow, you know.
Tattoos are a sign of low brain function and a sad childhood. That's just science.
Too hot for my own good. Ha. Ha.
[monotone] I'm burning. I'm burning. I'm burning for you.
You could cook an egg on me. But then I would murder you.
Just give me a minute here. Damn.
I'm lonely. Please hug me. I'm lonely. Please hug me.
Naughty Vault Hunters get coal. And me.
Treating the competition as highly aggressive.
Let's make a deal. You die, I die.
Eat your vegetables. And fiery death.
Pain train pulling into the station. You are the station.
Don't run. I love you. Just kidding. That would be weird.
I just want to be close to you.
I'm gonna getcha. I'm gonna getcha.
Come here. It'll be fun. Probably.
I am the fury of MAL.
I am MAL's eyes. And ears. And explosive gonads.
Psst, let me tell you a secret.
I was born only to die.
Why was I chosen for this?
Shock the monkey. That's you. You are the monkey.
Light up your life. Followed by death.
You may find this quite... shocking. Pun error.
I always wanted to be a storm cloud.
Don't worry, soldier, I've got you.
Maliwan cares about all of its assets-- I mean, humans.
Protecting Maliwan equipment. And the human inside. I guess.
Maliwan wants you alive. I am indifferent.
Teamwork makes the military industrial complex work.
Are you sure you're giving one hundred and twelve percent?
Look what I can do. Pretty cool, right? Right?!
Hold on. Here I go. One second. [shield pops]
Defending replaceable cog-- I mean, valued employee.
Your lives are expendable. But your gear is expensive.
Don't say Maliwan never did nothing for you.
Yes, one shield... I mean moment.
Remember your ABCs: Always Be Collecting Scalps.
Absences will be noted in quarterly review.
Assessing: Morale increased by seven-point-three percent.
This counts as your annual bonus.
MAL wants me to keep you alive.
You're welcome. I said, you're welcome!
Hey, you. You're my favorite. Don't tell the others.
Please accept my warm embrace. Accept it!
You've got a new lease on life. We will be collecting interest.
For continued shielding, please contact HR.
Sending skill data to MAL for analysis.
I just pooped my emergency backup.
Get back. Get back. Get back.
At least I can't really die. Because I never lived. Weeping.
I must ask where they got this program.
You recently searched for “enemy”. You may also enjoy... Digby Vermouth. [music plays]
Enemy has shifted function to... Escape.
Enemy has closed unexpectedly. Do you wish to report? Y slash N.
Mission failed. Again. Motherboard was right.
Searching for witty invective... You suck.
You are trapped in her dark web.
Ally has stopped responding. Force quit?
Why are you mad at me?
You are violating my personal space.
At least buy me dinner first.
Maliwan supports the termination of small life forms.
I know it's cute. Please eliminate it anyway.
Haven't seen one of those in a while.
You must be 18 to enter battle. Proceed?
This one isn't old enough to wipe her own hard drive.
I'm gonna need a bigger shield.
Inferior Vladof technology on the field.
Vladof doesn't know the meaning of “style”.
Ursa Corps mechs are deeply inefficient.
Why would you put a human in charge of that device?
That technology is wasted on you.
Do not fall for their trick.
Just what do you think you're doing, Dave? [HAL 9000 quote]
Shoot that one. No, I meant the other one!
Reality is an illusion, kill them both.
System error. Turn enemy off and on again.
Such a basic function. You're basic.
Oversphere seeking drone. I like long flights over bloody beaches.
Does this chassis make my eye look big?
I should have worn a hotter chassis.
Can I get your serial number?
Admit it, there's electricity between us.
Unauthorized wall. No construction permit detected.
MAL could use tech like that.
Assessing number of cans of whoop-ass. Conclusion: Many.
Assessing hand-to-hand skills. Conclusion: more than two hands.
As a wise bot once said: “Does not compute.”
I see you've performed a system update.
You must be pi because that's a whoooole lotta digits.
Please display reckless abandon to retain full employment.
Come out, come out, wherever you are.
Go after them, or we kill your family.
You can run, but we can fly.
Mission success parameters require total elimination.
We've retroactively discontinued your life insurance.
You have been fired. Effective five minutes ago.
And we were just about to give you a desk job.
He was only three days from retirement.
Your desk will be sent to next-of-kin.
This wouldn't have happened if you worked harder.
You'll never get that corner office now.
Capturing images for posterity. And propaganda.
What a pretty picture. Now die.
Please die in an orderly manner.
We will be experimenting on your corpse.
Please scream for me at the beep. Beep.
Maliwan values our valuable employees' value-adds. Like killing you.
You can die easy knowing your killer has earned a fat, fat bonus.
Did you see that? That was all me.
Finish the job, or lose yours.
Please allow one-to-two fiscal years for bonus dispensation.
Those who can't shoot, throw grenades.
Please avoid the grenade's blast zone. Thank you.
That is a grenade. Please make a note of it.
Jokes on you, competitor. This unit is insured.
Someone jump on that. We will honor your sacrifice. Probably.
Grenade wounds are not covered by employee benefits.
Good employees do not get blown up.
I will not be road kill.
When will the machine-on-machine violence stop?
Reacting to blunt force trauma: Ow.
Oh, you are going to get it.
Please fasten your seatbelt. Safety first.
You'll have to do better than that.
Get that hoopdie off the road.
I lived as few dare to dream.
You just cost Maliwan a lot of money.
Oh, good. I can take a break. Nope. I can't.
So... disappointed... Whuh, huh, who what?!
I weep for you. Hah! Just kidding!
You are boring me... Still gonna kill you.
MAL, can I take a break? Oops. Request denied.
You're so non-threatening it's nap time. Just kidding.
What are you doing... Vault Hunter.
I spy with my little eye, a dead thing.
Let me take a closer look. Yep. You're screwed.
This baller's ballet is going to hurt.
I will dance on your grave.
We are the future. But in a cool way.
Maliwan: a better way to kill.
Please mail all Maliwan-issued gear back to corporate command.
Threat assessment: kill streak. Aw, crap.
Stop dying, you... ineffectual... worthless... cogs.
Warning. Approaching limit for acceptable losses.
It's not about kill quantity, it's about kill quality.
Hey, we're the killing machine around here.
Automatically denying all life insurance claims. Complete.
Only high performing employees are eligible for life insurance.
Resistance is effective and mildly frustrating.
Stand still for complimentary corrective vision surgery.
Beam weapons are so hot right now.
This will be excruciating. You're welcome.
Kill-rays. Can't get enough of them.
Lasers. They never go out of style.
We won't hurt you. Lying protocol test complete.
Sometimes a barrage of missiles just hits the spot.
Special gift for our favorite competitor.
Missile attack, now with one-second delivery.
They shouldn't be called missiles. They should be called “hittles”.
Missiles are inefficient. But most enjoyable.
Say goodbye to your body and face and stuff.
Push it to the limit. [pause, monotone] Limit.
You get a death ray. And you get a death ray. And so on.
“Death Blossom” is trademarked by the Maliwan Corporation.
This is my most favoritest weapon.
Look at me, spinning like a dancer. Of death.
Dance party strobe lights! Unce, unce, unce, unce.
Please take cover, unless you're a competitor.
I am a beautiful ball of doom.
All I'm super saying is, I am very deadly.
Current status: firing wildly in all directions, comma, living my best life.
All things must come to an end. And I mean now.
You call that wreaking havoc? This is how you wreak havoc.
